          results from <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">0.67</NUMEX> to <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">1.5</NUMEX> to be accurate. The accuracy of
          <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">physicians</ENAMEX>' estimates of CHD risk after therapy with
