          <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">estimation</ENAMEX>, we compared the mean relative
          <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">over</NUMEX>-estimations for scenarios using <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX> with the
          factor compared with scenarios of <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX> without the
