          <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">physician</ENAMEX> estimate <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">7.8</NUMEX> times <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Framingham</ENAMEX> estimate),
          <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">intermediate</ENAMEX> for medium risk scenarios (<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">2.8</NUMEX> times), and
          smaller (<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">1.5</NUMEX> times) for high-risk scenarios. Table 2shows
