        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Chatellier et al</ENAMEX> provided clinical information about <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">66</NUMEX>
        <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX> to <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">6</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">physicians</ENAMEX> and asked the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">physicians</ENAMEX> to
